Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:33.83,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}终于找到了  全新的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:37.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}日月却来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:43.34,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}我前往的地方  不是“未来”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:47.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仅仅不停地追赶着“过去”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:53.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}不停地鸣响着 那过去的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:57.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仿佛无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:03.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}差不多了吧  那厌倦搜索的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:08.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}丢掉心里的纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:13.49,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  总有会停的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:18.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这么漫长  却如此冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:24.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  为什么会选择我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:28.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}笼罩着我  真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:33.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  已经忘了停
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:38.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天依然持续下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:43.82,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在默默撑开的雨伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:55.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}接近那温暖的怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要撇下你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是战友的墓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是伊修瓦尔人的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样被扔在了路边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我心中 伊修瓦尔的战争还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许一生都无法终结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把父亲的研究托付给你的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:00:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈愿国民的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.21,0:00:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定进入士官学校的也是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使得到了不愿见到的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也无法逃离现实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远无法彻底偿还
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.06,0:01:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个请求 马斯坦古先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的后背烧毁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能做…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果无法偿还的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少为了阻止新的火焰之炼金术师诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.95,0:01:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想破坏背上的秘传
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 请解开禁戒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从父亲让我背负的东西中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我从炼金术中解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.51,0:02:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽量烧得不留伤痕的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是对着谁举枪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们俩的时候 大佐都是叫我莉莎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是这种关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你上当 恩维
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就倒在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 一枪接一枪的 你射得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你弄成破抹布 扔到大佐面…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我重要的部下做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太逞强了 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过由我来解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的人类 别从上往下看…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的本体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真丑陋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩维这名字 就是嫉妒的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫉妒确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑陋的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我的视线中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是做什么 中尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的由我收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下一击就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把枪拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能服从
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您放下手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须给予它最残忍的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我连你的右手一起烧掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面和你比个高低
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在这之前 你看看自己的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想摆着这副脸成为国家的元首吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐想达成的目标不是这样的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面的人保护更下面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是小小的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能做到这点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:08:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺有趣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就搭你这条船了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看看你那幼稚的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么改变这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让欲望控制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落入畜生之道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你要活在复仇之中 我不会阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有阻止别人复仇的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是被憎恨束缚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在众人之上的话 会建立什么样的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真值得看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让大佐杀恩维
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不打算让它活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于走到这一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既不是为了国家也不是为了伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是为了报仇雪恨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是被仇恨所蚕食
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能堕落到那一边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想开枪就开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 开枪杀了我之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不打算自己一个人活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让带来疯狂的火焰之炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连同我的身体一起从这个世上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个情况是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惹小孩生气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经是仇敌的人对我说教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又让你经历了一段痛苦的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是群笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴上说那么多好听的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩人情游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人反胃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们人类是那么伟大的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺着本能做自己想做的事情呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古大佐 你没忘记吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡可是想取你性命的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像杀死小不点青梅竹马的父母的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是斯卡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了对了 那个东方之都的女孩子和狗的合成兽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是斯卡杀了他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在伊修瓦尔那么多同胞被杀的仇恨都去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称做“鹰之眼”上了兴头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她杀尽了你的同胞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有更好的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:12:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多豪华的阵容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憎恨 痛哭 杀和被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒地翻滚吧 趴在地上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然友好地拉着手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些低级东西怎么可能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 小不点 霍克爱 马斯坦古 斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 啊 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩维…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在嫉妒人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类应该比你们人造人要弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使被打 即使精疲力竭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走错道路 快要倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管多少次都会再次站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围的人会帮他站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在羡慕这样的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍弃小 保住大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微想一想就不难理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做就没法开枪了吧 人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这才是你们人类的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 要变身的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是年轻漂亮的好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类真愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在无所谓的事情上赌命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 如果硬挤出去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经活不长了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然变得像破抹布一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你们人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你们这些最低级的存在 随便摆弄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 居然还是被低级中的低级小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 可恶 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:16:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恩维…居然在羡慕人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恩维…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恩维…居然被这种小鬼看透
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屈辱之极
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这之后 你那些道理还能支撑多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就尽管去努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自决了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口自己愈合了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得正是时候 快帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么帮忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们接受了枪杀阿姆斯壮少将的命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少将 连少佐也在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得正是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始这里由我指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 现在快帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把头低下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子弹不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摧毁上颚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样至少不会被咬死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人一组一定要干掉一只
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看中央士兵的勇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了女将军
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能用单手 果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样会被打死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁去帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我弟弟还没弱到吃了这点攻击就会死的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艺术性的肌肉与艺术性的炼金术组合攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Excellent and Elegant
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 阿姆斯壮家已经全空了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 他们就是在这里组装战车的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是正门上层
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告作战本部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们遭到了布里克斯战车的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战本部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别喊了 我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 打回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 居民的避难还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等那屁事完毕的话 正门就被攻下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令部 联络正门炮击队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然对着市区开炮？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也用收音机播放出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那装备是布里克斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么到这里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原中央司令部勤务
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆力不错的好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常精确地记得这里的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.24,0:22:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后有一个人帮我们挖了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.31,0:22:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从市区到这里的地道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能有人能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.48,0:22:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被问是谁 我一般回答是主妇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.49,0:22:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我报上另一个名号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.14,0:22:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.29,0:23:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你会把那对兄弟带来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.41,0:23:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教训一个顽皮的小鬼 不需要那么多人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.74,0:23:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 烧瓶中的小人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.65,0:23:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给了我一部分身体的奴隶23号
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次你来成为我身体的一部分吧


